---
layout: root.njk
pageClass: intro
---

{% include "components/logo.njk" %}
<main>
  <section class="page-intro__about">
    <img
      src="./assets/tiny-janusz.png"
      alt="a face drawn by a modestly talented man-child"
    />
    <p>
      Hi there, I'm <a href="https://sonnet.io">Rafał Pastuszak</a>. Untested is
      my digital garden. It's where I learn, share what I've learned, and work
      with the garage door up (<a href="/111">more</a>).
    </p>
    <blockquote>
      <em>untested</em> like <em>undead</em>, so not
      <em><strong>not</strong>-tested</em>, but in a limbo causing constant fear
      and anxiety, boooo!
    </blockquote>
  </section>
  <section class="page-intro__contact">
    {% include "components/widget-subscribe.njk" %}
  </section>

  <section class="page-intro__feed">
    <header class="page-intro__section-nav">
      <h2>Articles</h2>
      <a href="/all">View all</a>
    </header>
    <ol class="timeline" reverse>
      {% for note in collections['untested-article'] | reverse %}
      <li class="timeline__item">
        <a href="{{ note.url }}">{{ note.data.title }}</a
        ><time>{{ note.page.date | dateFormat('dd·MM·yyyy')}}</time>
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ol>
  </section>
</main>

